# 4. Capability-First Feature Key Rule

Feature keys must be **capability-first**, not vendor-first.

## Correct pattern
```text
research.start
research.generate_strategies
research.background_processing
results.export.csv
results.export.dossier
results.shortlist
contacts.enrich_person
companies.find_similar
crm.sync.import
crm.sync.export
billing.manage_subscription
```

## Incorrect pattern
```text
contacts.enrich_lusha
research.ai_generate_strategies_openai
```

## Exception
Provider names are allowed only in:
- provider catalogs
- provider requirements
- provider management screens
- integration configuration

But not in product capability keys.

