# 6. Role Matrix

Use this role model consistently.

## Platform Operator Roles
These can manage platform-level configuration.

```text
owner
billing_admin
developer
```

They can manage:
- integrations
- provider/API configuration
- platform features
- billing
- subscription
- module configuration

## Workflow Roles
These can operate the business workflow.

```text
owner
admin
manager
analyst
member
developer
billing_admin
```

### Notes
- `billing_admin` may access workflow pages if desired, but is not a workflow operator by default
- `admin` is a business admin, not a technical platform operator
- `developer` is allowed in both sets

## Page access baseline

| Area | Allowed Roles |
|------|---------------|
| Dashboard | all organization members |
| CRM Opportunities | workflow roles |
| Mandates | workflow roles |
| Research | workflow roles |
| Results | workflow roles |
| Companies | workflow roles |
| Contacts | workflow roles |
| Integrations | platform operator roles |
| Billing | platform operator roles |
| Settings | owner, admin, developer, billing_admin as needed |

