# 9. UI Interpretation Rules

## Modules
Modules control:
- sidebar visibility
- route visibility
- page-level access

## Features
Features control:
- actions
- exports
- embedded widgets
- premium enhancements
- provider-backed actions

## Hidden workflow stages
Concepts like:
- discovery
- shortlist
- dossier generation
should appear as:
- internal workflow state
- embedded view
- action
- secondary tab

not as top-level modules by default

